{"tid":2439913,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"強國復星幾時同BioNTech研發咗疫苗？","createTime":"2021-03-09T14:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T16:12:25.000Z","uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c299001552a188957dfd832c5a23321e4a07a95","tid":2439913,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"明明Pfizer課金俾BioNTech<br />\n大家50 50<br />\n新聞稿冇咗Pfizer之餘，仲變咗復星研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2021/03/20210307/20210307_131256_471.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2021%2F03%2F20210307%2F20210307_131256_471.html&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=ee7fcdec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2021/03/20210307/20210307_131256_471.html</a><br />\n<br />\n逾75萬劑復必泰疫苗抵港<br />\n2021年3月7日<br />\n<br />\n逾75萬劑由復星醫藥與BioNTech合作研發的復必泰疫苗今日運抵香港，連同上月底抵港的585,000劑疫苗，已有合共約1,343,000劑復必泰疫苗運抵本港。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n疫苗抵港後，工作人員隨即檢查和核對疫苗，確保疫苗符合產品規格和冷鏈運輸標準。政府會把疫苗存放在經驗證的超低溫冷藏櫃，按藥廠指定的溫度妥善保存。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n屬五個優先組別的市民可在網上預約本月10日至30日的接種名額，在七間由醫院管理局營運的社區疫苗接種中心接種復必泰疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n優先組別市民也可在網上預約八間接種科興疫苗的接種中心、醫管局轄下18間普通科門診診所直至3月28日的名額，或自行向參與疫苗接種計劃的私家醫生和診所預約接種科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n市民可透過地理資訊地圖和2019冠狀病毒病互動地圖儀表板搜尋所有疫苗接種地點，包括社區疫苗接種中心、醫管局普通科門診診所，以及參加疫苗接種計劃的私家醫生和診所。"},{"pid":"37061c84ede891c469fb414b5e6c250a1a7e4c72","tid":2439913,"uid":359504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202012160276.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202012160276.aspx&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=f517e8e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202012160276.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"26d068bcb7994f3695a56364ced14f563f057530","tid":2439913,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37061c84ede891c469fb414b5e6c250a1a7e4c72","tid":2439913,"uid":359504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202012160276.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202012160276.aspx&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=f517e8e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202012160276.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"開發喎"},{"pid":"03817ce6ac50a69f9b51c92835e903ed6e069cb4","tid":2439913,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26d068bcb7994f3695a56364ced14f563f057530","tid":2439913,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37061c84ede891c469fb414b5e6c250a1a7e4c72","tid":2439913,"uid":359504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202012160276.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202012160276.aspx&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=f517e8e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202012160276.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"開發喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"據公告，2020年3月，復星醫藥與BioNTech簽訂協議，獲得BioNTech授權在中國大陸及港澳台獨家開發、商業化基於BioNTech專有的mRNA技術平台研發的COVID-19疫苗產品。<br />\n<br />\n好亂呀！"},{"pid":"b3bc12b25ca8c5697b53963ebc7bc6d3ab2a3fa3","tid":2439913,"uid":365791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:15:00.000Z","msg":"biontech同全球好多國家都有合作研發疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知各國間嘅技術係點保密"},{"pid":"37c84e33235d5e02d0df109ca44c4ed0f8651899","tid":2439913,"uid":173002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:58:38.000Z","msg":"[url<a href=\"https://www.dw.com/zh/%E8%B0%81%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%86bnt162%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97/a-55578952][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fzh%2F%25E8%25B0%2581%25E7%25A0%2594%25E5%258F%2591%25E4%25BA%2586bnt162%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%2Fa-55578952%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=edde08e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dw.com/zh/%E8%B0%81%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%86bnt162%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97/a-55578952][/url]</a><br />\n德國新聞訪問BioNTech負責人，BioNTech係同輝瑞合作研發BNT162，即係一般所講嘅輝瑞疫苗，完全無提過強國嘅復星，復星根本無參與過哩款mRNA疫苗嘅研發。如果疫苗配方俾復星改咗，同輝瑞唔同，即係全部臨床測試都要做過嗮，起碼要多大半年，所以復星自稱合作開發嘅復必泰其實都係輝瑞疫苗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全世界都係由輝瑞挪註冊，只有強國要經復星做代理商，強國唔俾BioNTech同輝瑞係境內做測試同申請註冊，一定要經強國公司，所以要搵復星搞強國申請註冊，改埋個中文名叫復必泰。<br />\n復星只係買咗強國嘅代理權，淨係做輝瑞疫苗嘅強國物流，但係復星同港共就煲成係復星開發，要歐美疫苗強國化，最搞笑嘅係強國成日假新聞話輝瑞疫苗死咗好多人，強國本身仲未批准輝瑞疫苗 ( 復必泰 )，所以復星仲未可以係強國生產所謂復必泰，復星至會要係德國挪貨俾港共。"},{"pid":"8afb7880b14085565a5344c16d5d195223979c04","tid":2439913,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T19:00:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dw.com/zh/%E8%B0%81%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%86bnt162%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97/a-55578952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fzh%2F%25E8%25B0%2581%25E7%25A0%2594%25E5%258F%2591%25E4%25BA%2586bnt162%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%2Fa-55578952&d=eGp%